.getting_started
  .content
    h2.section-title Getting Started

    = responsive_image("_includes/million.jpg", class: "million poster")
    .details
      p.p Still is still in early active development. To get started:

      pre.p
        code
          | mix archive.install hex still_new
          br
          | mix still.new mysite

      p.p
        ' This will create an Elixir project in the folder
        span.code mysite
        '. Youâ€™ll find an
        span.code index.slime
        '  file inside
        span.code priv/site
        ' .

      p.p
        ' Run
        span.code mix still.dev
        '  to start the development server. Then open
        span.code http://localhost:3000
        '  in your web browser to see the new website.

      p.p
        | You can also add it to an existing project.
        br
        | Visit our docs for all the goodies.
    = responsive_image("_includes/mean.jpg", class: "mean poster")
